data.description: Nestled in the sought-after Park at Camden, this home is a haven of luxury and comfort. As soon as you step inside, you're welcomed by inviting wood floors that add warmth and style to every corner.    The large open kitchen is where the magic happens. Picture stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, upgraded white cabinets, and a massive island waiting for your culinary adventures. And get thisCothe kitchen flows right into the family room, making it the ultimate spot for relaxing with family and friends.    Upstairs, the owner's suite is like its own little escape.  A custom walk-in closet is practically begging to be filled with all your favorites, plus a spa-like bath with all the trimmingsCoa tile shower, garden tub, and dual vanities. With two additional bedrooms, everyone gets a space of their own.  Bonus: there's even a loft space, perfect for gaming or getting some work done. More Photos are coming soon!  And let's not forget about the spacious two-car garageCoperfect for keeping your vehicles safe and secure while also providing extra storage space.  And of course, the fenced backyardCoa perfect spot for your furry friends to roam and play while you enjoy some fresh air  Whether you're hosting a gathering or simply unwinding with family, this home sets the stage for countless happy memories. Welcome to your new oasis!    Close to shopping, Highway 92, and I-575
